<body id="send_body">


    <div class="top_bar">
        <a href="/tutorial" class="tutorial" >Tutorial</a>


        <div class="top_img">
            <a href="/profile"><img src="/icons/logo.png" alt="" id="top_bar_logo"> </a>
        </div>
      
            <a href="/logout" class="tutorial" id="tutorial"> Logout</a>
    </div>

    <button type="button" id="back_button" class="red" onclick="go_back()">Go Back</button>

    <p class="section_title">
        1. Create Clients
    </p>



        <div class="box">
            <p class="box_title">Add Client</p>
            <img src="/icons/client.png" alt="">
            <button onclick="add_client()">+</button>
        </div>

 

    


        <p class="tip">Click on the +, and create a Client.</p>


        <p class="section_title">
            2. Create Exercises
        </p>

        <div class="box">
            <p class="box_title">Add Exercise</p>
            <img src="/icons/exercise.png" alt="">
            <button onclick="add_exercise()">+</button>
        </div>

        <p class="tip">Click on the +, and create an exercise.</p>

        <p class="tip">*NOTE: Create multiple exercises before next step, since workouts contain multiple exercises.</p>

        <p class="section_title">
            3. Create Workout
        </p>

        <div class="box">
            <p class="box_title">Add Workout</p>
            <img src="/icons/workout.png" alt="">
            <button onclick="add_workout()">+</button>
        </div>

        <p class="tip">Click on the +, and create a workout using the exercises you made.</p>




        <p class="section_title">
            4(Option 1)  Send Workout
        </p>

        <div class="box">
            <p class="box_title">Send Workout</p>
            <img src="/icons/phone.png" alt="">
            <button onclick="send_workout()">Send</button>
        </div>

        <p class="tip">Click on Send and then chose the workout you want to send a click get link. Copy the link and send it to your Clients!</p>




        <p class="section_title">
           4 (Option 2) 7-Day Plan
           </p>

           <div class="box">
            <p class="box_title">Create 7-Day Plan</p>
            <img src="/icons/calendar.png" alt="">
            <button onclick="create_plan()">+</button>
        </div>

        <p class="tip">Click on +, and then select the client who you are making the plan for, and the select a workout for each day of the week!</p>


        <div class="box">
            <p class="box_title">Send 7 Day Plan</p>
            <img src="/icons/mail.png" alt="">
            <button onclick="send_plan()">Send</button>
        </div>

        <p class="tip">Click on send, and then choose the client whos plan you are trying to send, then click get link the copy the link and send it to them!</p>




